{"h6e224a16gce9eg4183gad62g3eee082b4df7": ["Astarion came for my neck. A vampire, if you can believe it. I gutted him for his effort.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "hce083c6cgfbe9g472ag8e86g1b83f6f47214": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "h60dcab7ega451g46b5gaab9g83a7b7eaf006": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "h8101f6aeg57b7g4324g8c83g92cd084fbfb1": ["Astarion sought to make a meal of me - a bloody <i>vampire </i>in our midst. I killed him, of course.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "h0c06cf40g3b46g47fdg8a37g17f2829fd203": ["I awoke to find Astarion's teeth upon my neck. He paid with his life.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "hfbbed7dagf205g4f64gb2e3g9a38938387af": ["|I killed Astarion because he was a vampire  (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "hd4b68d0fgede2g47e2g8d69g4bf9b3abe041": ["|I killed Astarion because he was a vampire  (Gale Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "h75e90697ged80g4130g8309g1af52b50e117": ["I caught Astarion trying to drink my blood last night. I took care of him, though. He'll never prey on the living again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "4b873657-fd32-46c5-93f4-3b42caf53bc4"], "h215ca42cga643g4786gab73gef620ecec6a4": ["A vampire? He needed to go, no doubt about it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "hcd1bcf5agc289g4e1fg9c74ga8f3be649a66": ["You acted quickly and justly - as the <i>ghaik</i> covet minds, so do vampires covet blood.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "hb913329cgb59eg4a9cg94a1g2739eedf946a": ["We had to get rid of him. We've enough parasites to handle without a vampire as well.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "he40631bbgf947g4eacgaf7fg389f587ca4f0": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "h58657ea7g440eg4a5fg8bceg170cb9d4317f": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "h7fd0b2a3gfa4dg4533g9f52g298cd102df33": ["|You did the right thing  (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "ha62b2542g3071g4382gb3e1g2de178500ed8": ["|You did the right thing  (Gale Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "hc1c3906cg3293g4a1fg97e8g925e4c5e35b0": ["A good choice - we could never have trusted him.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "67fbbcd9-5a07-4c48-8795-7518b9dd084d"], "h17cc5d76gb951g4814gaebag0a7e51eff2ff": ["Astarion was a vampire. He needed to go, no doubt about it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "8d754c78-7e03-4709-ab3d-9ed71f59cdfb"], "h24a72c87g1c59g4794ga27dgb56ed9f92504": ["You acted quickly and justly - as the <i>ghaik</i> covet minds, so do vampires covet blood.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "8d754c78-7e03-4709-ab3d-9ed71f59cdfb"], "hb1eb1b2cg251fg4545g8b2egdc1ef3e7f9c5": ["Yes. We had to get rid of him. We've enough parasites to handle without a vampire as well.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "8d754c78-7e03-4709-ab3d-9ed71f59cdfb"], "h6d9c538fg9937g4d36gb193g9285e47e6e00": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "8d754c78-7e03-4709-ab3d-9ed71f59cdfb"], "h3676d5f1g4a87g45edg8e7cgf25b663eba69": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "8d754c78-7e03-4709-ab3d-9ed71f59cdfb"], "he0c194ecgf4b2g42a0gb977g10d4022afb57": ["| I agree. I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "8d754c78-7e03-4709-ab3d-9ed71f59cdfb"], "hb682c843g4026g49e3g8879g8cf04ff13fbb": ["| I agree. I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Ref