m away, of course.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "ab9d09bd-480f-a23f-17b4-7c87bbb9fc87"], "h05f8017bgf8a8g49deg8e4dg0313bd463c0f": ["I awoke to find Astarion's teeth upon my neck. I spared his life - but sent him away.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "ab9d09bd-480f-a23f-17b4-7c87bbb9fc87"], "hf9980f15g3b28g4ffdga044g7b902d9c05f8": ["|I drove Astarion away because he was a vampire.  (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "ab9d09bd-480f-a23f-17b4-7c87bbb9fc87"], "hbf177052gc132g460egb37agad49b1e621a7": ["|I drove Astarion away because he was a vampire.  (Gale Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "ab9d09bd-480f-a23f-17b4-7c87bbb9fc87"], "h1152c197g0becg4813gbb17gf4ef0e05d825": ["I caught Astarion trying to drink my blood last night. I drove him off, though - we won't see him again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\GLO_Astarion_RD_VampireRevelation.html", "ab9d09bd-480f-a23f-17b4-7c87bbb9fc87"]}